          "method": "POST",
          "bodyParametersJson": "={ \"contents\": [{ \"parts\": [{ \"text\": \"You are the business analyst for PrintHub Africa, a Nairobi printing company.\\n\\nAnalyse this month's complete business data and produce:\\n1. Executive summary (key wins, key concerns)\\n2. Revenue analysis with MoM comparison\\n3. Product performance (stars, dogs, risers, fallers)\\n4. Customer analysis (LTV trends, churn signals)\\n5. Operational insights (production efficiency, stock)\\n6. Top 5 actionable recommendations for next month\\n7. Forecast for next month based on trends\\n\\nBusiness data:\\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\" }] }], \"generationConfig\": { \"maxOutputTokens\": 3000 } }"
        },
